                                                <li>Computer Science and IT</li>
                                                <li>Law</li>
                                                </ul>
                        
                                            </div>
                                            <p style="color: #ffffff; padding-top: 10px; ">NUS, NTU, and SMU are globally recognized for their programs in engineering, technology, business, management, and computer science.</p>

